description.en:
GAMI WORLD is the crypto platform which offers to interact with multiple
modules with the same token, includes several DeFi products, aims to
fulfill multiple needs on a single platform and has 6 modules in it.
It keeps expanding its ecosystem with “one token, multiple utilities” motto.
